Fri Jun 12 19:08:45 UTC 2026 - Fabian Vogt <fabian@ritter-vogt.de>

- Update to 6.7.0:
  * New bugfix release
  * For more details see https://kde.org/announcements/plasma/6/6.7.0
- Changes since 6.6.91:
  * Update version for new release 6.7.0
  * WordWrap: Fix enum parsing (kde#521210)
  * kirigami/Chip: Fix icon position, add Mnemonics, change color
  * popups: Add tooltip text color (kde#521024)
  * input/css/breeze: Match DialogButtonBox spacing to desktop style
  * input/css/breeze: Remove horizontal padding from checkbox/radio/switch (kde#520156)
  * output/quick: Use nearest filtering for Icon's texture (kde#520155)
  * text-wrap-mode: Use QTextOption enum (kde#520918,kde#520154)
  * WidgetStyle: Disable X-KDE-CustomElements (kde#520776)
  * Add themerc files
  * Don't install a .so link for internal libraries
- Drop patches, now upstream:
  * 0001-Don-t-install-a-.so-link-for-internal-libraries.patch

