Thu May 28 18:45:17 UTC 2026 - Fabian Vogt <fabian@ritter-vogt.de>

- Update to 6.6.91:
  * New bugfix release
  * For more details see https://kde.org/announcements/plasma/6/6.6.91
- Changes since 6.6.90:
  * Heading: use Heading kirigami template as base and don't override color
  * Set the Union Widgets output enabled again
  * Update version for new release 6.6.91
  * output/quick: Set menu popup type to Item
  * output/quick: Add a Changed event to Positioner and use it in PositionerLayout (kde#518917)
  * Place exported targets into Union:: namespace
  * CMake config file: fix required dependencies, include targets file
  * Use KDECompilerSettings, not KF-only KDEFrameworkCompilerSettings
- Add patch to avoid unnecessary .so files:
  * 0001-Don-t-install-a-.so-link-for-internal-libraries.patch

